# Node.js Toolchain

Pinned versions (single source: `package.json` → `engines`):

| Tool | Version | Also defined in |
|------|---------|-----------------|
| Node.js | **24.15.0** (LTS Krypton) | `.nvmrc`, `.node-version` |
| npm | **11.12.1** | `packageManager` |

When bumping Node/npm, update **all** of the above plus CI uses `node-version-file: .nvmrc`. Run `npm run check:engines` to validate the lockfile.

Local setup: `nvm install && nvm use` or `fnm use`.
